				{
					"Type": "NodeText",
					"Data": "Add --asset to search the content index of asset files (PDF/Word/Excel/txt etc.); use --ext to filter by extension (repeatable). In this mode --method only supports 0-3, and --order-by values are 0 relevance-desc, 1 relevance-asc, 2 updated-asc, 3 updated-desc."
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"ID": "20260704120100-feff4a0",
			"Type": "NodeCodeBlock",
